<div class="mailer-main-body" style="padding: 45px;background-color: #eee;">
  <p>
  <div class="heading-miler-name" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">Hello <%= @resource.fullname %>,</div>
  <%= @resource.invitor.fullname %> sent you an invitation to use Piccati. Once you are connected at Piccati you have access to view, select and manage your events image gallery from anywhere in the world. 
  <br>
  <div class="heading-notice-mailer" style="padding-top: 5px;padding-bottom: 20px;">
     Accept the invitation by clicking on the link below and set your password.
     <br>
     <%= link_to t("devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept"), accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @token) %>
     <br>
     Team Piccati wishes everlasting relationship between photographers and clients.      
  </div>
  <div>Regards,</div>
  <div class="heading-mailer-name" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">Team Piccati</div>
</div>